t_size": 20.0, "lines": ["追いかけてくれて", "うれしかったよ。"]}, {"box": [638, 954, 666, 1047], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["帰ろっか。"]}], "img_path": "148.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [305, 76, 333, 161], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ねぇ西片。"]}, {"box": [43, 314, 83, 366], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["何？"]}, {"box": [679, 618, 738, 732], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["西片が", "投げるなら、"]}, {"box": [144, 624, 261, 776], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["私に", "避けて欲しい？", "受け止めて", "欲しい？"]}, {"box": [421, 1000, 469, 1117], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ドッジの", "話だよね．．．？"]}, {"box": [96, 1006, 144, 1083], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ドッジの", "話だよ。"]}], "img_path": "149.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [769, 73, 794, 228], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["別にどっちでも．．．"]}, {"box": [454, 100, 507, 245], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["絶対に", "当ててみせるし。"]}, {"box": [379, 63, 410, 118], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["へえ、"]}, {"box": [693, 548, 745, 635], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["ふーん", "そっかー。"]}, {"box": [278, 554, 304, 633], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["へえー"]}, {"box": [97, 258, 181, 371], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["意外と強いと", "強引なとこ", "あるんだね。"]}, {"box": [44, 698, 67, 1080], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["「からかい上手の高木さんの・完ー"]}, {"box": [620, 935, 671, 1069], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ドッジボールの", "話だよね！？"]}, {"box": [203, 944, 251, 1078], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ドッジボールの", "話だよ。"]}], "img_path": "150.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [], "img_path": "151.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [632, 39, 761, 77], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["おまけ"]}], "img_path": "152.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [255, 104, 277, 192], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["オレ．．．？"]}, {"box": [304, 526, 364, 610], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["どうした", "あんっ"]}, {"box": [118, 628, 147, 710], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["い．．いや"]}], "img_path": "153.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [735, 169, 786, 249], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["はい"]}, {"box": [255, 117, 347, 285], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["西片全然！！", "一人にならない", "んだもん"]}, {"box": [725, 632, 755, 721], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["じゃあね"]}, {"box": [692, 883, 755, 1037], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["おーい", "どうした西片"]}, {"box": [97, 900, 169, 1067], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["いいや", "何でもない！！"]}], "img_path": "154.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [82, 36, 552, 304], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["しかちかい上手の高木さん。", "はいはいいときのかわいいの", "マンガの・イラスト"]}, {"box": [522, 226, 589, 268], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["問部"]}, {"box": [613, 124, 774, 254], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["第！！！"]}, {"box": [576, 87, 823, 301], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["あ．．．！！！"]}, {"box": [2, 302, 178, 604], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["書籍"]}, {"box": [185, 515, 244, 614], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["＆"]}, {"box": [159, 318, 339, 882], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["グランプリ作品は．．．", "えっ"]}, {"box": [56, 925, 189, 975], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["詳しくは"]}, {"box": [45, 1017, 316, 1073], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ゲッサン本誌・"]}, {"box": [59, 1101, 313, 1126], "vertical": false, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ｈｔｔｐ：／／＠ｅｋｋａｎｓｕｎｄｏｒ：ｎｅｒ："]}, {"box": [326, 1007, 791, 1075], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＷｉｎｄｏｗｓＤｉｘｔＶｅｒ"]}, {"box": [372, 1103, 768, 1123], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ｈｔｔｐｓ／／ｗｗｗ．ｐｉｘｉｖｎｅｔ／ｃｏｎｔｅｓｔ／ｇｅｓｓａｎ２．"]}], "img_path": "155.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [692, 24, 813, 549], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["『からかい上手の", "高木さん、"]}, {"box": [62, 16, 281, 163], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＫｕｃｈｏｌｏＷｉ－", "いや．．．ってＳｕｂａｌｅｌ"]}, {"box": [700, 441, 830, 697], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["小此宗"]}, {"box": [558, 618, 622, 832], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["誰にも言えない", "秘密があるのです．．．"]}, {"box": [84, 629, 110, 1154], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["マン二集団「あかね組」。優等生ツバキの秘密とは．．．？"]}, {"box": [692, 753, 841, 1087], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["肌が", "んな"]}, {"box": [763, 1029, 793, 1060], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}], "img_path": "156.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [0, 0, 342, 873], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["推", "メチャがワゴ口丁", "私は"]}, {"box": [206, 806, 308, 850], "vertical": false, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["最窓ガール"]}, {"box": [261, 799, 429, 877], "vertical": false, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["秘密コメディー！"]}, {"box": [554, 685, 755, 876], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["コミックス", "第１）巻", "大好評発売中", "！！！"]}, {"box": [220, 885, 747, 1164], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ソバキの", "胸の内", "山本崇－"]}, {"box": [432, 1076, 797, 1169], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["一良", "一度寝てるケンサンス３０５０年度の「本格的」ＨＰＨＰ"]}], "img_path": "157.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [12, 535, 847, 694], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["「次ページから電子版特別作録として『シノーツバヤの物の中、", "「スページから食べ放射から数とした『スノーツバキの胸の内第１話を視線！！"]}], "img_path": "158.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [639, 111, 686, 210], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["サザンカと", "アサガオが、"]}, {"box": [135, 144, 163, 239], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["脱走だと？"]}, {"box": [646, 608, 697, 741], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["すみません．．．！", "先生！！"]}, {"box": [237, 645, 315, 779], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["気付いたら", "布団がもぬけの", "殻で．．．"]}, {"box": [101, 643, 174, 739], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["おそらく", "外に行った", "のかと．．．"]}, {"box": [58, 1078, 235, 1116], "vertical": false, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["第１話も行けないから"]}], "img_path": "159.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [], "img_path": "160.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [77, 1057, 337, 1110], "vertical": false, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["だい", "第１話", "危険な男"]}], "img_path": "161.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [715, 72, 793, 169], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["すぐ私が", "連れ戻して", "来ます！！"]}, {"box": [358, 75, 429, 195], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["当たり前だ", "お前の班員", "なんだからな。"]}, {"box": [197, 71, 275, 205], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["おい、誰か", "２〜３人ついて", "行ってやれ。"]}, {"box": [110, 94, 150, 209], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["はーい"]}, {"box": [685, 475, 737, 553], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["すぐ準備", "します！"]}, {"box": [172, 506, 192, 601], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["まったく．．"]}, {"box": [700, 801, 798, 935], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["よりによって", "あおい組が", "山で夜間授業", "している日に．．．"]}], "img_path": "162.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [694, 56, 720, 153], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["あおい組！？"]}, {"box": [563, 58, 616, 174], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["汚らわしい", "男共が山に！？"]}, {"box": [55, 70, 159, 225], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["あのバカで", "アホで短気で", "くさいという山の", "向こうのサルが！？"]}, {"box": [640, 386, 745, 523], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["男って", "体はでかいけど", "脳はちっさい", "らしいわよ。"]}, {"box": [120, 382, 193, 505], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["とりあえず", "股間が急所で", "弱いらしいわ。"]}, {"box": [658, 827, 687, 888], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["男が．．．"]}, {"box": [43, 568, 121, 702], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["言葉遣いが", "乱暴なんだって"]}, {"box": [66, 815, 97, 880], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["山に．．．"]}], "img_path": "163.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [444, 42, 547, 319], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["バカ者！！", "男を甘くみるな。"]}, {"box": [721, 539, 798, 635], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["いつも", "言っている", "だろう。"]}, {"box": [593, 527, 641, 663], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["奴らは力が強く", "残虐性も高い。"]}, {"box": [112, 520, 185, 636], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["なめていると", "痛い目を", "みるぞ！！"]}, {"box": [378, 779, 452, 875], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["まぁ．．．", "わかれば", "よろしい．．．"]}, {"box": [235, 810, 272, 869], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["先生。"]}], "img_path": "164.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [706, 232, 765, 318], "vertical": false, "font_size": 13.0, "lines": ["いや．．．", "．．．", "ふ", "．．．", "いやいや．．．いいのでいい"]}, {"box": [363, 66, 416, 221], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["私一人で行っても", "よいですか。"]}, {"box": [207, 50, 314, 187], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["私の班のことで", "他の人に迷惑", "かけるのも", "悪いですし．．．"]}, {"box": [303, 534, 383, 660], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["今、みんな男に", "ビクついて", "いるしな．．．"]}, {"box": [23, 528, 123, 646], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["それは．．．", "先生に", "ビクついて", "いるんだと．．．"]}, {"box": [697, 536, 751, 692], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["お前なら一人でも", "大丈夫か．．．"]}, {"box": [429, 554, 450, 656], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["いいだろう。"]}, {"box": [620, 900, 671, 989], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["では", "頼んだぞ。"]}, {"box": [65, 898, 121, 1024], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["必ず２人を", "捕まえて来い。"]}], "img_path": "165.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [760, 89, 795, 155], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["はい。"]}, {"box": [153, 161, 282, 403], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["あかね組くノーツバキ、", "必ずやサザンカ、", "アサガオの２人を", "連れて帰ります。"]}, {"box": [597, 611, 649, 699], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["行って", "参ります。"]}, {"box": [614, 903, 629, 947], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["．．．．．"]}, {"box": [139, 1016, 221, 1096], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["何事も", "なければ", "いいが．．．"]}], "img_path": "166.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [270, 76, 301, 137], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["男が．．．"]}, {"box": [44, 50, 71, 108], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["山に．．．"]}, {"box": [616, 474, 636, 606], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["いけません．．．！"]}, {"box": [660, 760, 707, 844], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["サザンカ", "アサガオ"]}, {"box": [121, 787, 172, 855], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["どうか", "無事で。"]}], "img_path": "167.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [752, 75, 802, 164], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["うーむむ", "眠いよー"]}, {"box": [337, 75, 390, 179], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["帰ろうよ", "サザンカー。"]}, {"box": [339, 332, 392, 447], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["何言ってるの", "アサガオ。"]}, {"box": [97, 333, 148, 507], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["姉さまにいいところ", "みせるのよ。"]}, {"box": [742, 700, 814, 850], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["そのためには", "あんたの戦闘力が", "必要なんだから"]}, {"box": [640, 710, 687, 813], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["シャキっと", "しなさいよ。"]}, {"box": [435, 796, 482, 892], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ムリだよー", "眠いもん。"]}, {"box": [269, 719, 324, 808], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["お腹も", "空いたし。"]}, {"box": [97, 699, 172, 815], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ホントに", "眠気と空腹に", "弱いわね．．"]}], "img_path": "168.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [667, 64, 742, 239], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["しょうがない", "そのへんで食べれる", "キノコでも探して．．．"]}, {"box": [158, 44, 179, 101], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["むにゃ"]}, {"box": [107, 486, 130, 576], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["アサガオ！？"]}, {"box": [667, 849, 746, 931], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ちょっと", "しっかり", "してよ。"]}, {"box": [369, 841, 425, 937], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["寝てる場合", "じゃ．．．"]}, {"box": [285, 1034, 304, 1143], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["アサガオ．．．？"]}], "img_path": "169.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [712, 55, 742, 119], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["大丈．．．"]}, {"box": [479, 63, 500, 92], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["わ。"]}, {"box": [469, 55, 510, 101], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["わ。"]}, {"box": [106, 440, 188, 541], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["今ので", "目が覚めた", "みたいね。"]}, {"box": [661, 741, 742, 849], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ねぇ私たち", "何してるん", "だっけ。"]}, {"box": [410, 858, 439, 905], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["は？"]}, {"box": [294, 728, 347, 809], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["頭でも", "打った？"]}, {"box": [161, 707, 235, 822], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["それとも", "ずっと", "寝てたの．．．？"]}], "img_path": "170.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [236, 192, 330, 312], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["男を", "探してんで", "しょーが"]}, {"box": [153, 97, 174, 163], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．"]}, {"box": [36, 369, 57, 435], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ふーん。"]}, {"box": [151, 564, 180, 626], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["男を．．．"]}, {"box": [640, 561, 697, 667], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["夜中に", "抜けだして、"]}, {"box": [194, 792, 228, 823], "vertical": false, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["！？"]}, {"box": [29, 827, 53, 888], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["あっ！！"]}, {"box": [283, 858, 349, 999], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["悪い子ですね", "サザンカ。"]}, {"box": [44, 1067, 71, 1112], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["ね．．．"]}], "img_path": "171.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [770, 57, 801, 148], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["姉さま！！"]}, {"box": [398, 100, 450, 233], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["捕まえましたよ", "サザンカ。"]}, {"box": [289, 65, 337, 189], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あ、ついクセで", "抱きついて．．"]}, {"box": [92, 419, 140, 496], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ホントに", "もう．．．"]}, {"box": [670, 605, 693, 637], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["て、"]}, {"box": [149, 632, 228, 784], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["何で男が", "山にいると知って", "いるんです"]}, {"box": [576, 921, 738, 1056], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["今日たまたま", "先生が話して", "いるのを", "聞いたんです"]}, {"box": [176, 894, 251, 1050], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["授業サボって", "いなくなってた時", "てすか？"]}, {"box": [104, 948, 124, 1033], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["まったく。"]}], "img_path": "172.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [637, 79, 715, 232], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["違います！！", "あれは姉さまに", "贈る花を摘みに．．．"]}, {"box": [563, 57, 589, 123], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["それで、"]}, {"box": [447, 66, 510, 140], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["男を", "探して、"]}, {"box": [308, 67, 383, 201], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["どうする", "つもりだったん", "ですか。"]}, {"box": [197, 33, 221, 129], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["サザンカ．．．"]}, {"box": [49, 213, 98, 330], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["あなた", "もしかして．．．"]}, {"box": [577, 603, 606, 666], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["男を．．．"]}, {"box": [142, 629, 168, 698], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["はい！！"]}, {"box": [48, 803, 134, 921], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["もちろん", "ぶっ倒す", "ためです！！"]}], "img_path": "173.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [786, 57, 800, 98], "vertical": true, "font_size": 14.0, "lines": ["．．．．．"]}, {"box": [486, 62, 540, 145], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["男は女の", "敵です！！"]}, {"box": [329, 83, 429, 257], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["近くまで", "来ているこの好機を", "みすみす逃す手は", "ありませんよ！"]}, {"box": [678, 460, 720, 554], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["とりあえず", "帰りますよ。"]}, {"box": [315, 458, 391, 575], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["先生", "カンカン", "なんですから"]}, {"box": [783, 792, 834, 890], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["まったく", "サザンカ．．．"]}, {"box": [704, 793, 750, 908], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["アサガオまで", "巻き込んで、"]}, {"box": [467, 818, 494, 922], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["悪い子です。"]}], "img_path": "174.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [688, 85, 734, 198], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["コメンなさい", "姉さま！！"]}, {"box": [253, 85, 359, 205], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["花を摘みに", "行ったことで", "姉さまに", "叱られて．．．"]}, {"box": [46, 52, 151, 205], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["それで、男を", "倒したら．．．", "褒めてもらえると", "思って．．．"]}, {"box": [536, 610, 613, 728], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["．．．無事で", "よかったです"]}, {"box": [175, 901, 255, 971], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["一緒に", "帰りま", "しょう。"]}, {"box": [161, 1030, 182, 1091], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["あれ？"]}], "img_path": "175.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [731, 63, 801, 179], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["サザンカ！！", "またウソ泣き", "ですか！？"]}, {"box": [284, 56, 359, 191], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["私の身を案じて", "くれるなんて", "うれしいです。"]}, {"box": [199, 67, 249, 138], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["でも", "大丈夫。"]}, {"box": [654, 515, 733, 631], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["男なんて", "私にかかれば", "一捻りです。"]}, {"box": [166, 516, 243, 623], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["あとで", "褒めて", "くださいね。"]}, {"box": [575, 842, 608, 997], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["サザンカ！"]}], "img_path": "176.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [629, 464, 663, 550], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["悪い子。"]}, {"box": [656, 908, 705, 1025], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ねー", "よかったの？"]}, {"box": [80, 905, 126, 967], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["何が。"]}], "img_path": "177.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [772, 50, 819, 164], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ツバキちゃん", "だまして．．．"]}, {"box": [524, 67, 577, 190], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["迎えに来て", "くれたんだよ。"]}, {"box": [388, 52, 468, 214], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["このまま帰っても", "先生に大目玉", "くらうだけなのよ。"]}, {"box": [110, 69, 162, 205], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["だったら手柄を", "立てないと。"]}, {"box": [663, 446, 743, 607], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["男を倒せば", "姉さまもきっと", "褒めてくださるわ。"]}, {"box": [208, 444, 230, 549], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["そうかなー。"]}, {"box": [767, 732, 787, 828], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["サザンカ！！"]}, {"box": [495, 766, 515, 862], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["アサガオ！！"]}, {"box": [115, 757, 145, 798], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["え。"]}, {"box": [353, 948, 404, 1064], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["もう", "追いかけて．．．"]}, {"box": [134, 964, 163, 1043], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["悪い子は、"]}], "img_path": "178.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [272, 65, 334, 237], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["無理やりにでも", "連れて帰ります。"]}, {"box": [125, 63, 200, 186], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ほらー", "ツバキちゃん", "怒ってるよー。"]}, {"box": [687, 405, 732, 491], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["まくわよ", "アサガオ。"]}, {"box": [155, 425, 203, 579], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ムリだと", "思うんだけどー！？"]}], "img_path": "179.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [742, 41, 768, 73], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["わ。"]}, {"box": [540, 203, 561, 288], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["やっぱり。"]}, {"box": [185, 35, 205, 118], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["アサガオ。"]}], "img_path": "180.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [321, 106, 366, 185], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["．．．あれ", "姉さま？"]}], "img_path": "181.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [714, 148, 773, 239], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["帰り", "ましょう。"]}, {"box": [237, 50, 264, 104], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["では、"]}, {"box": [756, 686, 802, 800], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ゴメンなさい", "姉さま。"]}, {"box": [592, 638, 642, 773], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["もうウソ泣きは", "効きませんよ。"]}, {"box": [447, 639, 526, 757], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["帰ったら", "せっかんです", "からね。"]}, {"box": [146, 688, 165, 767], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["えぇー"]}, {"box": [477, 949, 530, 1057], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["お腹", "空いたよー。"]}, {"box": [107, 935, 162, 1095], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["多分明日は", "ごはん抜きですよ。"]}], "img_path": "182.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [691, 65, 743, 171], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["死ぬよ", "そんなのー。"]}, {"box": [538, 42, 617, 161], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["私連れて", "来られただけ", "なのにー。"]}, {"box": [255, 65, 313, 146], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["連帯責任", "です。"]}, {"box": [166, 36, 214, 114], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あんまり", "だよー。"]}, {"box": [31, 39, 80, 137], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["じゃあ", "姉さまも！？"]}, {"box": [627, 400, 708, 543], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["私は班長", "ですから一番", "重いでしょうね。"]}, {"box": [115, 403, 143, 489], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["で．．．では、"]}, {"box": [612, 696, 714, 814], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["男を", "ぶっ倒して", "手柄を立て", "ましょうよ！"]}, {"box": [479, 687, 559, 825], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["姉さまも", "せっかんは", "イヤでしょう！？"]}, {"box": [296, 717, 378, 830], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["私の任務は", "あなたたちの", "捕獲です"]}, {"box": [165, 748, 243, 849], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["真面目", "すぎますよ", "姉さま。"]}, {"box": [23, 990, 94, 1126], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あなたが", "不真面目すぎる", "だけです！"]}], "img_path": "183.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [753, 84, 775, 182], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["だいたい．．．"]}, {"box": [702, 563, 729, 608], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["ん？"]}, {"box": [435, 526, 458, 640], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["クナイの音．．．"]}, {"box": [271, 527, 300, 632], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["男ですかね。"]}, {"box": [684, 956, 734, 1090], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["行きましょうよ", "姉さま！！"]}, {"box": [104, 978, 144, 1065], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["男が．．．"]}], "img_path": "184.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [448, 32, 485, 100], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["男が．．．"]}, {"box": [329, 77, 382, 155], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ほら早く", "姉さま！！"]}, {"box": [45, 55, 118, 207], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["せっかんを", "免除してもらう", "チャンスですよ！"]}, {"box": [640, 453, 718, 605], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ホントは姉さまも", "男をぶっ倒し", "たいんでしょう！？"]}, {"box": [282, 481, 332, 562], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["すぐ．．．", "そこに．．．"]}], "img_path": "185.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [630, 372, 770, 494], "vertical": false, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["．．．こさまへは", "．．．"]}, {"box": [427, 808, 470, 904], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["見たい．．．？"]}, {"box": [410, 1050, 466, 1114], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["あ．．．", "いや．．．"]}, {"box": [130, 1050, 158, 1112], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["あの．．．"]}], "img_path": "186.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [665, 79, 745, 279], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["そっか！！立場上", "直接言うとマズイんで", "ボヤかしてるんですね。"]}, {"box": [316, 97, 345, 282], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["忘れてください！！"]}, {"box": [570, 564, 591, 624], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["えぇ？！"]}, {"box": [226, 542, 249, 696], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["私としたことが．．．"]}, {"box": [28, 561, 56, 675], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["つい本音が．．．"]}, {"box": [547, 917, 676, 1021], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["男はバカで", "アホで", "うるさくて", "汚くて", "マヌケだと"]}, {"box": [181, 937, 260, 1034], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["そう先生に", "教えられて", "来たのに．．．"]}], "img_path": "187.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [749, 57, 801, 231], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["なぜなんでしょう", "最近．．．"]}, {"box": [289, 77, 369, 212], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["男のことを", "知りたいという", "思いが、"]}, {"box": [101, 359, 161, 442], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["胸の中で", "大きく．．"]}, {"box": [686, 603, 734, 718], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["なんだか", "顔も熱いし．．．"]}, {"box": [101, 598, 181, 718], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["私は", "おかしいんで", "しょうか．．．"]}, {"box": [661, 958, 712, 1094], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["行きましょうよ", "姉さま！！"]}, {"box": [165, 924, 216, 1081], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ダメと", "言ったでしょう？！！"]}], "img_path": "188.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [672, 84, 718, 219], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["じゃあほら！", "偵察だけでも！！"]}, {"box": [241, 30, 271, 89], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["偵察．．．"]}, {"box": [117, 181, 143, 278], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["見るだけ．．．"]}, {"box": [561, 439, 639, 580], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["こ．．．こんっ", "今後のために．．", "確かに．．．"]}, {"box": [105, 473, 214, 595], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["姿を確認して", "おいた方が、", "いいかも", "しれませんね。"]}, {"box": [706, 901, 732, 1026], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["行きましょー。"]}, {"box": [309, 900, 391, 999], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["何を言って", "るんですか", "私は："]}, {"box": [206, 882, 253, 979], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ダメですよ", "ダメ！！"]}, {"box": [32, 1019, 115, 1155], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["今まで真面目に", "生きてきたじゃ", "ありませんか"]}], "img_path": "189.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [793, 55, 811, 100], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}, {"box": [482, 84, 533, 219], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["見るだけですよ", "絶対に．．．"]}, {"box": [402, 52, 421, 174], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["もちろんです。"]}, {"box": [690, 515, 736, 600], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["やるわよ", "アサガオ"]}, {"box": [210, 521, 240, 602], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["何を．．．？"]}, {"box": [107, 522, 154, 643], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["見るだけって", "言ってたよね。"]}, {"box": [667, 719, 748, 837], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["バカね立場上", "そう言ってる", "だけよ。"]}, {"box": [483, 714, 565, 832], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["本音は", "男をぶっ倒せ", "よ。"]}, {"box": [358, 754, 406, 830], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["そうなの", "かなー。"]}, {"box": [93, 699, 121, 877], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["神様お許しください。"]}], "img_path": "190.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [721, 130, 745, 225], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["見るだけ．．．"]}, {"box": [385, 154, 437, 289], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["見たらすぐに．．", "帰りますから．．．"]}, {"box": [124, 462, 148, 571], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["この先に！？"]}, {"box": [310, 775, 350, 862], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["男が．．"]}], "img_path": "191.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [663, 71, 718, 150], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["誰かいる", "のか？"]}, {"box": [434, 530, 456, 588], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あれ？"]}, {"box": [680, 850, 732, 949], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["ちょっと", "姉さまー！！"]}, {"box": [583, 860, 624, 1017], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["男をぶっ倒すんじゃ", "なかったんですか！？"]}, {"box": [234, 853, 284, 950], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["やっぱり", "ダメです！！"]}, {"box": [114, 868, 190, 1020], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["というか何を", "聞いてたんですか", "サザンカ！"]}], "img_path": "192.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [32, 527, 847, 693], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["「続きは絶賛配信者の単行本第１巻でお率いみください」", "「続きは絶賛出信中の車をお楽しみください！」"]}], "img_path": "193.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [131, 94, 602, 142], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["からかい上手の高ホさんの"]}, {"box": [133, 180, 568, 203], "vertical": false, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ゲッサン少年サンデー・コミックススペシャル"]}, {"box": [196, 547, 516, 567], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["２０１８年７月１７日初版第１刷発行"]}, {"box": [439, 513, 762, 528], "vertical": false, "font_size": 13.5, "lines": ["０９－１２８３３０－６", "ＩＳＢＮ９７８－４－Ｃ"]}, {"box": [196, 657, 261, 680], "vertical": false, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["者", "著"]}, {"box": [199, 726, 262, 787], "vertical": false, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["発行者", "ＦＩＦＵフィ"]}, {"box": [137, 823, 545, 931], "vertical": false, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["「ゲッサン」２０１８年１月号〜６月号掲載作品", "連載担当／高長佑典", "単行本編集責任ノ鳥光裕", "単行本編集ノ高長佐典〈三輪張子（アイブロダクション）"]}, {"box": [402, 650, 665, 748], "vertical": false, "font_size": 25.333333333333332, "lines": ["山本禁一曲", "ＣＳｏｃｈｉｒｏＴａｎａｍａｎｏｎｏｒ２０１８", "．．．"]}, {"box": [407, 767, 617, 783], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["中央精版の印刷株式会社"]}, {"box": [142, 942, 240, 979], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["発行所"]}, {"box": [256, 943, 599, 962], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["〈〒１０－＊８０１）東京都千代田区一ツ橋二の三の"]}, {"box": [138, 1027, 762, 1142], "vertical": false, "font_size": 14.0, "lines": ["●法本には十分注意しでおりますが、印刷、製本なと製造上の不備がございましたら「制作局コール", "センター「パフリーダイヤルＩＤＥ３８６－６８２にご連絡ください。", "〈電話受付は、土・日・提供日を除く９，３０〜１７：８０", "●本書の一部または全部を無断で複製、転載、複写（コピー）、スキャン、デジタル化、上演、放送", "等をすることは、著作権法上での例外を除き禁じられています。代行業者等の第三者による本書の", "電子的複製も認められておりません。"]}, {"box": [425, 965, 741, 1018], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["２０１８年１１月１５日－編集ＯＲ（２３２）「９７２５", "平成２８年１０月１８日、現在は５８０１５年６月１５日（京都）大会社小学館"]}], "img_path": "194.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 847, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [120, 817, 145, 910], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.5, "lines": ["著発", "昔、"]}, {"box": [137, 849, 174, 877], "vertical": false, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["警者名"]}, {"box": [160, 813, 196, 917], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["名名行"]}, {"box": [215, 816, 520, 909], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["からかい上手の高木さん。９", "山本祟一朗", "株式会社小学館"]}, {"box": [123, 993, 574, 1020], "vertical": false, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["電子書籍制作会社株式会社昭和ブライト"]}, {"box": [219, 919, 723, 946], "vertical": false, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["〒１０１－８００１東京都千代田区一ツ橋２－３－１"]}, {"box": [123, 1065, 661, 1106], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.5, "lines": ["Ｘ収録されている作品は、執筆された当時の状況や年代を考慮の上、", "初回掲載時の表現のまま掲載されております。ご了承ください。"]}], "img_path": "195.jpg"}]}